---
import ZhLayout from '../../../../layouts/ZhLayout.astro';
---

<ZhLayout
  title="静电消除系统 | DGSDK 史帝克"
  description="史帝克专业静电消除系统：离子棒、离子风机、离子鼓风机等，适用于电子、SMT、包装、印刷、纺织、塑料和自动化工业生产线。"
  canonical="https://www.dg-sdk.com/zh/products/static-eliminator"
>
  <section
    class="products-hero"
    style="background: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.28), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18)), url('/assets/img/static-eliminator/bg-2.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;"
  >
    <div class="container products-hero-inner">
      <span class="products-hero-kicker">史帝克产品系列</span>
      <h1>静电消除系统</h1>
      <p>
        专业静电控制解决方案，适用于电子、SMT、包装、印刷、纺织、塑料和自动化工业生产线。
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="products-overview-section">
    <div class="container products-overview-layout">
      <aside class="products-sidebar">
        <div class="products-sidebar-box">
          <h3>产品分类</h3>
          <a href="/zh/products">所有产品</a>
          <a href="/zh/products/static-eliminator" class="active-category">静电消除系统</a>
          <a href="/zh/products/cleaning-machine">工业清洁机</a>
          <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts">精密加工零件</a>
          <a href="/zh/products/automation">自动化设备</a>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <div class="products-main">
        <section class="apple-product-section">
          <div class="apple-card-grid">
            <a href="/zh/products/static-eliminator/st-g-series" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/static-eliminator/st-g.jpg" alt="ST-G 智能静电消除棒" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">静电消除</span>
              <h3>ST-G 智能静电消除棒</h3>
              <p>高性能离子棒，实现稳定高效的静电消除。</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/zh/products/static-eliminator/st-e-series" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/static-eliminator/st-e.jpg" alt="ST-E 智能离子棒" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">静电消除</span>
              <h3>ST-E 智能离子棒</h3>
              <p>适用于小型工业集成的可靠静电控制设备。</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/zh/products/static-eliminator/st-f-series" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/static-eliminator/st-f.jpg" alt="ST-F 智能离子棒" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">静电消除</span>
              <h3>ST-F 智能离子棒</h3>
              <p>适用于连续生产线的快速响应离子化解决方案。</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/zh/products/static-eliminator/st-s200" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/static-eliminator/st-s200.jpg" alt="ST-S200 迷你离子风机" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">静电消除</span>
              <h3>ST-S200 迷你离子风机</h3>
              <p>适用于工作台和敏感应用的紧凑型防静电风机。</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/zh/products/static-eliminator/st-101a" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/static-eliminator/st-101a.jpg" alt="ST101A 台式离子鼓风机" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">静电消除</span>
              <h3>ST101A 台式离子鼓风机</h3>
              <p>桌面防静电风机，适用于工作台稳定运行。</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/zh/products/static-eliminator/st-104a" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/static-eliminator/st-104a.jpg" alt="ST104A 卧式离子鼓风机" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">静电消除</span>
              <h3>ST104A 卧式离子鼓风机</h3>
              <p>卧式离子送风，适用于更大防静电覆盖范围。</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/zh/products/static-eliminator/st-1200" class="apple-product-card">
              <img src="/assets/img/static-eliminator/st-1200.jpg" alt="ST1200 卧式离子风机" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="apple-card-tag">静电消除</span>
              <h3>ST1200 卧式离子风机</h3>
              <p>宽幅静电控制，适用于工业工作台和生产线。</p>
            </a>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="related-categories-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="related-cat-title">完善您的生产线</h2>
      <p class="related-cat-desc">静电消除器与表面清洁和自动化解决方案配合使用效果最佳。探索我们的相关产品类别：</p>
      <div class="related-cat-grid">
        <a href="/zh/products/cleaning-machine" class="related-cat-card">
          <img src="/assets/img/cleaning-machine/polarizer-cleaner.jpg" alt="工业清洁机" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="related-cat-info">
            <h3>工业清洁机</h3>
            <p>在静电敏感工艺前去除颗粒和污染物。</p>
            <span class="related-cat-link">查看产品 →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/zh/products/automation" class="related-cat-card">
          <img src="/assets/img/automation/product-a.jpg" alt="自动化设备" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="related-cat-info">
            <h3>自动化设备</h3>
            <p>将静电控制集成到全自动生产线中。</p>
            <span class="related-cat-link">查看产品 →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts" class="related-cat-card">
          <img src="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/precision-bearing-bracket-cnc-milled.jpg" alt="精密加工零件" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="related-cat-info">
            <h3>精密加工零件</h3>
            <p>用于设备集成和结构支撑的定制CNC零件。</p>
            <span class="related-cat-link">查看产品 →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ZhLayout>
